entries.title: Miss Universe crowns first Filipino American winner
entries.description: R'Bonney Gabriel - a fashion designer, model and sewing teacher from Texas - has become the first Filipino American to win Miss Universe.

entries.title: British man among dozens killed in Nepal plane crash
entries.description: A British man was among dozens of people killed in a plane crash in Nepal on Sunday.

entries.title: Man dies after crashing limousine into iconic Berlin landmark
entries.description: A Polish man has died after crashing a limousine into the Brandenburg Gate in Berlin.

entries.title: Italian actress Gina Lollobrigida dies aged 95
entries.description: Italian actress Gina Lollobrigida has died at the age of 95, according to ANSA news agency.

entries.title: Why an absence of A-listers at Davos is not just deep trouble for the WEF, but for globalisation
entries.description: Davos, the World Economic Forum (WEF) and its founder, Klaus Schwab, have become more famous than ever before in the past couple of years - albeit not for the reasons they might have wanted.

entries.title: Ukrainian player signs for Chelsea - and his former team pledges millions to war effort
entries.description: Ukrainian football team Shakhtar Donetsk has pledged millions of pounds to its country's war effort, after Chelsea FC signed one of its star players.

entries.title: Capture of 'last godfather' after 30-year hunt could end 'mafia myth'
entries.description: The capture of mafia boss Matteo Messina Denaro today was 30 years in the making.

entries.title: Italy's most wanted mafia boss arrested, police say
entries.description: Italy's most wanted mafia boss, Matteo Messina Denaro, has been arrested by police after 30 years on the run.

entries.title: At least five killed and eight missing in Chinese chemical plant explosion
entries.description: At least five people have died and another eight are missing after a massive explosion at a chemical plant in north-eastern China, according to state TV in the country.

entries.title: Black box and cockpit voice recorder from plane that crashed in Nepal found
entries.description: The black box and cockpit voice recorder of the plane that crashed in Nepal have been found, a Kathmandu Airport official has said.

entries.title: Rescuers resume search after Nepal plane crash - as day of mourning observed
entries.description: Rescuers have resumed searching for four people still missing after Nepal's deadliest plane crash in 30 years, officials have said.
